{
  "stem": "11964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the conditions for-- the sanitation conditions, were you able to bathe?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were you able to have toilets?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, bathing was really not considered necessary any longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to wash.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Skimpily, we used to wash.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some apartments had toilets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some apartments had outhouses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you asked the first question, I remember what it was about--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sanitation.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sanitation was very poor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because sanitation was very poor, there was an epidemic of typhus, or typhoid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because we had only one doctor in the ghetto and we had no hospitals, we had a very, very high death rate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many people died like flies, because they were telling us that the typhoid was carried by lice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't really deal with lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody had lice in their hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were saying that if you put turpentine on you hair, you can kill the lice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was just not doable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just not doable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We really didn't have the wherewithal to deal with an epidemic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I'll tell you an incident that I write about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I developed very sharp pains in my abdomen, and the one doctor we had diagnosed it as very acute appendicitis.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I needed to have surgery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father, through some connections, connected with it friend of his, a Polish policeman, who took a note from my father to a surgeon in town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he begged him to operate on him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took me out in a, in a wagon which was used to taking corpses to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they covered me with straw and rags.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took me at night out to a back entrance to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the surgeon met me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
